[package]

categories = []

features = ["postgres", "chrono", "r2d2", "uuidv07"]

[dependencies.protobuf]

features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio]

[dependencies.tonic]

features = ["tls"]
optional = false

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "0.7.4"

[dev-dependencies]
mockall = "0.9.0"

bin = []
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[package]
name = "protobuf"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.1.0"

authors = ["cobbinma <cobbinma@gmail.com>"]
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
prost = "0.7.0"
tonic = "0.4.0"

[build-dependencies]

[lib]

doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc_macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2018"
